snippet.title: Amber Heard Reveals Marrying Johnny Depp To Steal His Money
snippet.description:
💙 Amber Heard Reveals Marrying Johnny Depp To Steal His Money
Depp was wrapping up nearly four days of testimony in his libel lawsuit against a British tabloid newspaper that accused him of violently assaulting Heard. The actor is suing News Group Newspapers, the publisher of The Sun, and the paper's executive editor, Dan Wootton, for an April 2018 piece in which he was referred to as a "wife-beater."
